giri kanye ( kannada : ಗಿರಿಕನ ಯೆ ) is a 1977 indian kannada drama film directed by dorai - bhagwan duo .   it is based on the novel of the same name by bharathisutha .   the film stars rajkumar , jayamala and vajramuni in lead roles .   the film was a musical blockbuster with all the songs composed by rajan-nagendra considered evergreen hits .   rajinikanth was initially selected to play the villain 's role which was eventually played by thoogudeepa srinivas .